name: you make the prize - a very special download kit
description:
You Make The Prize
a beautiful download to print & put together

a heartfelt collaborative project from Shanna Murray & Cecelia Hayes

Declare your love with a gorgeous, from-the-heart prize ribbon. We've put together more than 20 ways to celebrate a sweetheart, a loyal friend, a beloved child, a long lost dear one, and even home sweet home.

There are so many ways and occasions to use our prize ribbon kit (well beyond Valentine's Day), we think it will be love at first sight! 

All projects can be put together with items easily found around the home or at your local craft store.

Each kit includes:

materials guide

28 illustrated elements - medallions, tags, and paper

step by step instructions, complete with guides and templates for making a variety of ribbons

two templates for beautiful boxes in which to present your prize

inspiration & encouragement to create your heirloom 


Upon purchasing your download kit an email will be automatically sent to you with a download link. Pages are formatted for an 8.5x11 piece of paper, easily printable from your home printer. Print as many times as you like for yourself.





Copyright Information:
In purchasing this download you acknowledge that it is for personal use only. All elements of this project including illustrations, instructions, and templates are original content, belonging to Shanna Murray and Cecelia Hayes. No portion of this download may be used for resale. Prize ribbons may not be reproduced for sale, and content may not be not be reused for any purpose other than personal use and gift giving.

name: gift packaging
description:
For a small fee we'd be happy to enclose your decal, instructions, and application tool in our kraft tube gift wrap. Just purchase this listing in addition to your decal and we'll take care of the rest! 

Please feel free to leave a message for a card enclosure in the Paypal comment box when you check out, we'll jot your message down for you and send everything along to the recipient.

Note: If purchasing more decals than you've purchased packaging for, please be sure to indicate which decal you'd like gift wrapped. 

Cheers!
